L’Éternel te bénira de Sion,","poem":1},{"lineBreak":true},{"text":"Et tu verras le bonheur de Jérusalem","poem":1},{"lineBreak":true},{"text":"Tous les jours de ta vie;","poem":1}]},{"type":"verse","number":6,"content":[{"lineBreak":true},{"text":"Tu verras les fils de tes fils.","poem":1},{"lineBreak":true},{"text":"Que la paix soit sur Israël!","poem":1}]}],"footnotes":[]},"thisChapterLink":"/api/fra_lsg/PSA/128.json","thisChapterAudioLinks":{},"nextChapterApiLink":"/api/fra_lsg/PSA/129.json","nextChapterAudioLinks":{},"previousChapterApiLink":"/api/fra_lsg/PSA/127.json","previousChapterAudioLinks":{},"numberOfVerses":6}